PHASE 2: FEATURE ENGINEERING
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

🔧 DOMAIN-DRIVEN FEATURE CREATION

Created 24 engineered features across 5 analytical domains:

📊 ECONOMIC DOMAIN (6 features)
├─ GDP_per_Capita: Wealth per person indicator
├─ Log_GDP: Economic scale (log-normalized)
├─ Log_Population: Population magnitude (log-normalized)
├─ Economic_Stress_Index: Inflation + unemployment pressure metric
├─ Inflation_Unemployment_Pressure: Combined economic headwinds
└─ Tax_Burden_Ratio: Government revenue burden index

🏥 HEALTHCARE DOMAIN (4 features)
├─ Healthcare_Stability_Score: Physician availability + mortality rates
├─ Mortality_Pressure_Index: Infant & maternal mortality combined
├─ Physician_Access_Score: Healthcare professional availability
└─ Healthcare_Access_Gap: Disparity in healthcare infrastructure

🎓 EDUCATION & WORKFORCE DOMAIN (4 features)
├─ Human_Capital_Index: Educational attainment composite
├─ Workforce_Stability_Score: Labor participation + engagement metric
├─ Education_Pipeline: Primary to tertiary education progression
└─ Education_Gap_Index: Educational inequality measure

👥 DEMOGRAPHIC DOMAIN (5 features)
├─ Urbanization_Rate: Urban population percentage
├─ Population_Pressure_Index: Birth rate + fertility pressure
├─ Dependency_Ratio_Proxy: Youth + elderly dependency burden
├─ Military_Burden: Armed forces as % of population
└─ Abs_Latitude: Geographic location (absolute latitude value)

🌍 ENVIRONMENT DOMAIN (5 features)
├─ CO2_per_Capita: Per-capita carbon emissions
├─ CO2_per_GDP: Emissions efficiency ratio
├─ Environmental_Pressure_Index: Resource stress composite
├─ Resource_Land_Balance: Agricultural to forested land ratio
└─ Fuel_Cost_Pressure: Gasoline price burden index

─ Total Engineered Features: 24
─ Combined with raw features: 59 total columns

