PHASE 4: MODEL TRAINING
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

🤖 THREE-MODEL ENSEMBLE APPROACH

Model 1: LogisticRegression
├─ Purpose: Interpretable baseline
├─ Hyperparameters: Multi-class='multinomial', solver='lbfgs'
├─ Training time: 0.02s
└─ Status: ✓ TRAINED

Model 2: RandomForestClassifier
├─ Purpose: Nonlinear ensemble benchmark
├─ Hyperparameters: n_estimators=100, max_depth=None, random_state=42
├─ Training time: 0.50s
└─ Status: ✓ TRAINED

Model 3: XGBClassifier
├─ Purpose: Primary production model (gradient boosting)
├─ Hyperparameters: n_estimators=100, learning_rate=0.1, random_state=42
├─ Sample weights: Applied (min=0.987, max=1.007) for class balance
├─ Training time: 1.68s
└─ Status: ✓ TRAINED

⏱️  TOTAL TRAINING TIME: 2.20 seconds (on 151 samples × 47 features)

